Texts.Eng: Bring the ^green;Genetic Material^reset; to ^orange;me^reset; at the ^orange;Science Outpost^reset;
Genetic material comes from many things, not just meat. Remember that if it is alive and full of cells, it just might give you some.
^orange;Meat^reset; is both delicious and useful. ^orange;Extract some meat^reset; and bring me 5 of the results.
